OL,3,CPotato farmer could lose 'a couple of
OL,4,Chundred thousand' with warning of
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FA Co Down farmer says he is set to
OL,8,Flose 'a couple of hundred thousand'
OL,9,Fpounds in sales as waterlogged fields
OL,10,Fmeans he is unable to harvest his crop.
OL,12,FPaul Hamilton is an eighth generation
OL,13,Fgrower, following in his family's
OL,14,Ffootsteps. However he told UTV that
OL,15,Fpersistent wet weather over the past
OL,16,Fnumber of months is severely affecting
OL,17,Fhis business.
