OL,3,CPotato farmer could lose 'a couple of
OL,4,Chundred thousand' with warning of
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,FMr Hamilton's warning comes as one Co
OL,8,FArmagh supplier has revealed that is
OL,9,Fis being forced to incur more costs by
OL,10,Fbringing in potatoes from countries
OL,11,Fsuch as Cyprus to meet demand.
OL,13,FHe said: "Speaking to my father and
OL,14,Ffrom my own experience, we've had
OL,15,Fplenty of wet summers, plenty of wet
OL,16,Fwinters, we've had plenty of wet
OL,17,Fsprings.
