OL,3,CPotato farmer could lose 'a couple of
OL,4,Chundred thousand' with warning of
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,7,F"It's costing around #3,000 an acre to
OL,8,Fgrow so over 30 acres is a loss of
OL,9,F#90,000 in terms of inputs.
OL,11,F"In regards of actual sales we are
OL,12,Ftalking a couple of hundred thousand
OL,13,Fhere."
OL,15,FWilson's Country in Craigavon, Co
OL,16,FArmagh, supply various retail outlets.
OL,17,FStuart Meredith from the company said
OL,18,Fthey usually like to see around 50% of
OL,19,Fcrops planted by the middle of April
OL,20,Fbut currently, there is 'very little'
OL,21,Fplanted.
